script.name: plugin.guilds.signal.kill
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = get global variable: name='pageid.guilds' $Guild.Data = get global variable: name='guilds.data'
* check if the sector should be contested if [THIS] -> is of class Station $sector.owner = [SECTOR] -> get owner race if $sector.owner == [OWNER] @ START [NULL] -> call script plugin.guilds.checkcontested : Sector=[SECTOR] Station Destroyed?=[THIS] end end
if [THIS] == [PLAYERSHIP] if not [THIS] -> is of class Astronaut if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Escape Pod in cargo bay $x = [THIS] -> get x position $y = [THIS] -> get y position $z = [THIS] -> get z position $escapepod = create ship: type=Escape Pod owner=Player addto=[SECTOR] x=$x y=$y z=$z $escape = move player to ship $escapepod: Teleport=[FALSE] skip if $escape $escape = eject player ship: to=$escapepod else if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Ejector Seat in cargo bay $escape = eject player ship: to=null end if $escape AND [PLAYERSHIP] != [THIS] [PLAYERSHIP] ->set invincible: enabled=[TRUE] $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=135 display notification: message=$read.text, icon=104 $speak = create new array, arguments=[Page.MiscVoice], 1271, [Page.MiscVoice], 1268, null START speak array: $speak prio=80 $task = [PLAYERSHIP] -> get next available task: starting=[Task.StartCustom] [PLAYERSHIP] ->start task $task with script plugin.guilds.escapepod and prio 100: arg1=null arg2=null arg3=null arg4=null arg5=null $flags = [Find.Friend] | [Find.Neutral] | [Find.DockingAllowed] | [Find.Nearest] $station = find station in galaxy: startsector=[SECTOR] class or type=Station race=null flags=$flags refobj=[PLAYERSHIP] serial=null max.jumps=5 $speed = [PLAYERSHIP] -> get max speed [PLAYERSHIP] ->set ship speed to $speed $shield = [PLAYERSHIP] -> get maximum shield strength [PLAYERSHIP] ->set current shield strength to $shield if $station -> exists START [PLAYERSHIP] -> command COMMAND_DOCKAT : arg1=$station, arg2=null, arg3=null, arg4=null end end end return null end
if [OWNER] == Player return null end
if [OWNER] == Guilds if [THIS] -> is of class Ship if [THIS] -> get job id $original.race = [THIS] -> get local variable: name='original.race' if $original.race [THIS] ->set owner race to $original.race end end end end
* check for bounty boost if [THIS] -> is of class Moveable Ship if $a.killer -> exists if $a.killer -> is of class Ship $killer.race = $a.killer -> get true owner else $killer.race = $a.killer -> get owner race end if $killer.race == Player if [PLAYERSHIP] -> get amount of ware Bounty Hunter Guild Licence in cargo bay if not [THIS] -> is of class Astronaut $sector.owner = [SECTOR] -> get owner race $licence = get licence ware: race=$sector.owner if $licence if [PLAYERSHIP] -> get amount of ware $licence in cargo bay $noto = get notoriety from race $sector.owner to race [OWNER] if $noto < [Notoriety.Foe] $payment = 10000 if [THIS] -> is of class M3 $payment = 20000 else if [THIS] -> is of class Huge Ship $payment = 50000 else if [THIS] -> is of class Big Ship $payment = 30000 else if [THIS] -> is of class Freighter $payment = 10000 else if [THIS] -> is of class Fighter $payment = 10000 else $payment = 10000 end add player money: $payment, transaction object=$a.killer, page=$page.id, textid=1028, [SECTOR], null, null, null, null end end end end end end end end
* check for constested sector if $Guild.Data if $a.killer -> exists $contested = $Guild.Data['contested.sectors'] if $contested if $contested[[SECTOR]] $tFaction = $contested[[SECTOR]][2] $killer.race = $a.killer -> get owner race if $tFaction[$killer.race] if [OWNER] != $killer.race AND [TRUEOWNER] != $killer.race $points = $tFaction[$killer.race][2]
$amt = 20
if [THIS] -> is of class M5 $amt = 20 else if [THIS] -> is of class M4 $amt = 50 else if [THIS] -> is of class M3 $amt = 100 else if [THIS] -> is of class M8 $amt = 150 else if [THIS] -> is of class M6 $amt = 250 else if [THIS] -> is of class M7 $amt = 350 else if [THIS] -> is of class M2 $amt = 500 else if [THIS] -> is of class M1 $amt = 400 else if [THIS] -> is of class TL $amt = 300 else if [THIS] -> is of class TM $amt = 200 else if [THIS] -> is of class TP $amt = 80 else if [THIS] -> is of class TS $amt = 80 else if [THIS] -> is of class Dock $amt = 2000 else if [THIS] -> is of class Factory $amt = 800 end
$vari = [THIS] -> get ship variation do if $vari == [Vari.Plus] $amt = $amt + ( $amt / 2 )
$points = $points + $amt $tFaction[$killer.race][2] = $points end end end end end end
return null

comment.var: check if the sector should be contested

sval.val: check if the sector should be contested
